Introduction

D.Holic was a girl group formed by Star Road Entertainment. They debuted on October 23, 2014 with the single "D.Holic Dark With Dignity".

On July 2, 2017, the group unofficially disbanded after members Nayoung and Youjin left the group, leaving only one member in it, Rena. Later, the last member was announced as a member of another group.
